  "text": "We are not currently dealing with object creation and deletion, but it is a straightforward extension to this translation, which is currently being automatized (using and extension of the XML-based languages GXL and GTXL [CITATION_1] ). An effort can be done to customize the translation to the application characteristics, in order to reduce the produced state space.",
